long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhances your experience with FC25 Ultimate Team web app with SBC Solver, Real time prices, Keyboard shortcuts & Autobuyer 

Features:
- SBC Solver 
- Keyboard Shortcuts 
- Autobuyer with captcha solver
       - Generate solutions based on club players
       - Generate solutions for entire SBC set based on club players
       - Generate solutions for all Daily SBCs set based on club players
       - Solve repeatable SBCs multiple times with single click
- Evolution suggestions based on club players
- UT Club players Analytics
